reviewText:
[This review is based on the 2006 Revised Edition DVD]
 Educational video targeted at exercise & health professionals.  It is a fairly tecnical lecture on the multiple health benefits of & advice related to resistance exercise in elderly.  The lecture is follows a series of information slides;  there are no actual exercises demonstrated (i.e. this is not a "workout video").
